  "detailed_description": "Step into the shoes of four fearless hunters to survive countless hordes of enemies, you can play with:<br><br><strong>Knight:</strong> An excellent melee combatant.<br><strong>Archer:</strong> Always ready to finish off everyone from a distance.<br><strong>Mage:</strong> Scholar of powerful magic.<br><strong>Cleric:</strong> With light and healing spells, prepared for survival.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681340/extras/2e3460eaa819f5363a6dd33fe7948cc1.poster.avif?t=1704727176\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681340/extras/2e3460eaa819f5363a6dd33fe7948cc1.webm?t=1704727176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681340/extras/2e3460eaa819f5363a6dd33fe7948cc1.mp4?t=1704727176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get ready to see:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Four maps, namely the forest, the snow, the desert, and the dungeon.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 30+ Different enemies for you to fight.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> </li></ul> Exclusive abilities for each hunter.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Mysterious merchant who will sell you improvements.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681340/extras/24f8a7194c83249a82146e2ddff0d08d.poster.avif?t=1704727176\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681340/extras/24f8a7194c83249a82146e2ddff0d08d.webm?t=1704727176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681340/extras/24f8a7194c83249a82146e2